spotlight.title: Spotlight
spotlight.description: Check out some of our biggest and most beloved titles.

289893.title: Traitor
289893.description: When an FBI agent investigates an international conspiracy, all clues lead to a former U.S. Special Operations officer in this gripping thriller.

292018.title: Capitalism: A Love Story
292018.description: Michael Moore looks at the global financial crisis and the U.S. economy during the transition between the incoming Obama Administration and the outgoing Bush Administration.

300175.title: Stand Up Guys
300175.description: After one of them gets paroled, three retired gangsters reunite and reminisce as another ponders his next job — killing his old friend.

301333.title: The Flowers of War
301333.description: Set during the 1937 Japanese invasion of Nanking, an American taking refuge in a church attempts to save a group of women from marauding soldiers.

301814.title: The Pink Panther 2
301814.description: Inspector Clouseau is back! This time, he's teaming up with a squad of international detectives to stop a globe-trotting thief from striking again.

302489.title: Penelope
302489.description: An aristocratic heiress just wants to find love, but one small flaw keeps getting in the way. Why does a pig's nose have to make things complicated?

307762.title: The Three Musketeers
307762.description: In this classic tale of friendship and heroism, a young, aspiring musketeer must team up with three legendary fighters to save France.

312170.title: Charlie Bartlett
312170.description: A cheeky high schooler sells prescription drugs to the kids of his new school while offering pseudo-psychiatric advice from a bathroom stall.

337827.title: New York, I Love You
337827.description: In neighborhoods all across New York City, a series of romantic stories unfold in the city that never sleeps, where love is on everyone's mind.

348454.title: Pathology
348454.description: Upon graduating from medical school, Ted Gray joins a lauded pathology program — but he suspects his colleagues may be too comfortable with death.

371078.title: A Most Wanted Man
371078.description: When a mysterious immigrant arrives in Hamburg, he attracts the attention of U.S. and German intelligence, kicking off a race to uncover the truth.

400849.title: Sunshine Cleaning
400849.description: A once-popular single mother-turned-maid gets a new lease on life when she gets into the lucrative world of crime scene cleanup with her sister’s help.

417714.title: Seeking Justice
417714.description: After a high school teacher's wife is brutally attacked, a stranger representing a vigilante group offers revenge on the attacker in exchange for a favor.

437415.title: Deadfall
437415.description: On the run after a casino heist, a brother and sister go their separate ways on divergent paths, making their inevitable reunion potentially deadly.

455866.title: Cliff Hanger
455866.description: Adrenaline-fueled skiers make harrowing descents in the Jackson Hole backcountry, shred neck-deep powder in Japan and face Wyoming's tallest peak.

456876.title: Bad Lieutenant: Port of Call New Orleans
456876.description: In the wake of Hurricane Katrina, a detective investigates the murders of several Senegalese immigrants.

456901.title: Trespass
456901.description: When thieves invade the upscale home of a clever diamond dealer and his wife and take them hostage, the captives must rely on their wits to survive.

456909.title: The Code
456909.description: A renowned burglar in debt to the Russian mob recruits a young thief to help him pull off one last caper: stealing a priceless pair of Faberge eggs.

456911.title: Survivor
456911.description: A foreign service worker in London goes on the run trying to dodge an assassin out to stop her from thwarting a deadly terrorist attack on New York.

456923.title: The Iceman
456923.description: Based on a shocking true story, a family man goes to great lengths to keep his work as a ruthless hitman a secret from the people he loves.

462750.title: Nothing but the Truth
462750.description: In Washington, D.C., a reporter faces a possible jail sentence for outing a CIA agent, taking her case all the way to the Supreme Court.

465289.title: Stone
465289.description: A prison official and a scheming inmate's lives become dangerously intertwined when the convict's seductive wife comes asking for favors.

465292.description: A young electrician assumes a dead man's identity and unwittingly finds himself trapped in an underworld game of Russian roulette.

465428.title: Gods of Egypt
465428.description: A mortal tries to save the world and his own true love by joining with a powerful god in an epic battle against his rival, the deadly god of darkness.

468376.title: The Joneses
468376.description: A superficially successful family buys their way into a ritzy neighborhood, but their high-rolling lifestyle costs them more than just money.

469606.title: The Paperboy
469606.description: A Miami reporter returns to his sultry hometown to dredge up the facts surrounding the case of a death row inmate, who may in fact be innocent.

472908.title: Odd Thomas
472908.description: In a small desert town, a fry cook with psychic gifts, his girlfriend, and the sheriff team up to stop a weird stranger from unleashing an evil force.

476215.title: Cosmopolis
476215.description: A 28-year-old billionaire takes a hypnotic odyssey through NYC in his limo, encountering incendiary riots and a parade of provocative characters.

477175.title: The Midnight Meat Train
477175.description: An aspiring photographer is drawn into the path of a subway serial killer.

480267.title: Transsiberian
480267.description: One of those legendary train trips that people used to dream about taking, the Transsiberian Express has probably seen better days. An American couple, Roy and Jessie, decide to return home the long way from their recent sojourn in Peking and meet another couple from the West, Carlos and Abby, with whom they quickly form that tenuous bond that often unites fellow travelers away from home. When Roy gets separated from the train at a stopover, Jessie begins to realize that their compatriots aren’t exactly who or what they seem to be. But the real dangers of their unforgettable trip have only begun to surface; Russian cops, mobsters, and locals are still to come.

480291.title: Triangle
480291.description: A woman's yacht trip turns to terror when she hits a storm in and her group is forced to board a seemingly deserted ocean liner to get to safety.

501714.title: Middle Men
501714.description: The story of Jack Harris, an internet commerce pioneer who battles his demons while dealing with con men, mobsters, drug addicts, and porn stars.

507477.title: The Ghost Writer
507477.description: A writer agrees to author the memoirs of a former Prime Minister only to learn that he is a war criminal and that his first writer was found dead.

507479.title: Gold
507479.description: A prospector out to strike gold gets a rare chance at his goal when he goes on an incredible trip to the Indonesian jungle with a gung-ho geologist.

507596.title: My Blueberry Nights
507596.description: A heartbroken young woman journeys across America to understand the truth about love, and meets some unexpected characters along the way.

516859.title: The Last Witch Hunter
516859.description: A fearless, immortal witch hunter ends up in a ferocious battle with supernatural enemies as he fights to save the human race from evil.

520281.title: The Immigrant
520281.description: A Polish immigrant, whose sister falls ill upon their arrival in America, falls prey to a charming but wicked man who forces her into prostitution.

522579.title: Kon-Tiki
522579.description: Despite a fear of water and inability to swim, a Norwegian explorer and his crew embarked on an epic journey across the Pacific on a balsa wood raft.

528074.title: Stolen
528074.description: In New Orleans, a thief just released from prison embarks on a frantic hunt for his daughter, who has been abducted and locked in the trunk of a taxi.

528599.title: Takers
528599.description: High-octane thriller about a group of notorious criminals whose streak of untraceable bank heists may come to an end thanks to a hardcore detective.

539272.title: Evil Dead
539272.description: This update to the classic horror flick finds five friends in a cabin, about to unlock the curses that live inside the Book of the Dead.

539677.title: Lion
539677.description: A young man makes an emotional journey to reconnect with his birth family in India after being tragically separated from them years earlier.

540148.title: My Bloody Valentine
540148.description: It’s been ten years since a string of murders plagued a small town. But when one of the survivors returns home, he discovers a familiar dread.

552216.title: Get the Gringo
552216.description: When a career criminal is nabbed by Mexican authorities and placed in a tough prison, he must  learn to survive, with the help of a young boy.

557221.title: Cop Out
557221.description: Bruce Willis and Tracy Morgan star as an oddball pair of NYPD partners who must take on a ruthless, memorabilia-obsessed criminal.

559457.title: Survivor (Español)
559457.description: Incriminada por crímenes que no cometió, una diplomática trata de impedir un ataque terrorista en Nueva York.

559458.title: The Code (Español)
559458.description: Un ladrón veterano contrata a uno más joven para ayudarle a hacer un último trabajo para saldar una deuda con la mafia rusa.

563168.title: Predators
563168.description: A mercenary reluctantly leads a group of elite warriors mysteriously brought together on a jungle planet where they are hunted by an alien race.

580530.title: Detroit
580530.description: This relevant, fact-based story, set in 1967’s Detroit riots, tracks a group of rogue cops, who respond to a call with vengeance instead of justice.

582081.title: Vicky Cristina Barcelona
582081.description: Two American women are taken in by the splendor of Spain, but not as much as they are drawn to a rugged painter and his sultry former lover.

587297.title: 6 Souls
587297.description: A psychiatrist treats a patient who takes on the personalities of his murder victims. In her attempt to help him, she puts herself in danger.

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

599603.title: Contagion
599603.description: Oscar®-winning filmmaker Steven Soderbergh (Ocean's Eleven films, Traffic) returns to large-scale cinema with this global action thriller that revolves around the threat of a deadly outbreak of a fatal disease and the people determined to keep it at bay. As the fast-moving epidemic grows, the worldwide medical community races to find a cure and control the panic that spreads faster than the virus itself. At the same time, ordinary people struggle to survive in a society coming apart. A stellar international ensemble cast including Academy Award® winners Matt Damon, Gwyneth Paltrow, Kate Winslet, Marion Cotillard and nominees Jude Law and Laurence Fishburne portray the dedicated doctors at the CDC and World Health Organization who rush to contain the outbreak of a new virus. Tracking its source to Hong Kong and searching for a cure, these determined Samaritans do their utmost to limit deaths, civil unrest and the false rumors surrounding the disease in this viral outbreak drama with multiple plot lines in the style of Soderbergh's Oscar®-winning narcotics drama Traffic.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619660.title: Ip Man 3 (English Dub)
619660.description: Hong Kong, 1959. A crooked real estate developer leads a band of gangsters in a property coup that can only be stopped by the Wing Chun grandmaster.

620866.title: The Tournament
620866.description: Skilled assassins face off against each other in a deadly 24 hour English tournament, where the winner claims a coveted cash prize.

620886.title: The Road
620886.description: Following an apocalyptic event, a father and son travel through North America’s dangerous terrain in the hopes of reaching the ocean.

637106.title: Unknown
637106.description: A man awakens from a coma after a car wreck to find his wife doesn’t recognize him, his identity has been stolen, and hitmen are trying to kill him.

639313.title: The Infiltrator
639313.description: Based on a true story, a U.S. federal agent goes deep inside the inner workings of a notorious drug trafficking cartel in order to take it down.

642286.title: The Physician
642286.description: To gain admittance to medical school, an 11th Century surgeon's apprentice disguises his true identity to move forward with his quest.

662955.title: Secret in Their Eyes
662955.description: A team of detectives is torn apart when one of their children is brutally murdered. The ensuing 13-year investigation ends with a shocking secret.

663814.title: The Sisters Brothers
663814.description: Brothers and assassins Eli and Charlie Sisters pursue a prospector across the American Northwest in this witty reimagining of the cinematic Western.

665877.title: Season of the Witch
665877.description: Two 14th-century Crusaders are tasked with routing a suspected witch to a distant monastery to let monks determine if she caused the Black Plague.

672287.title: The Angry Birds Movie
672287.description: When mysterious green piggies visit an island populated by flightless birds, it's up to three unlikely outcasts to figure out what the pigs are up to.

682050.title: I Kill Giants
682050.description: Barbara Thorson, a young woman struggling with life, is the only thing that stands between terrible giants and the destruction of her small town.

684133.title: The Man Who Knew Infinity
684133.description: Based on the true story of the academic career of an obscure Indian mathematician whose groundbreaking theories changed mathematics forever.

684136.title: The Killer Inside Me
684136.description: A charming small town sheriff is slowly unmasked as a dangerous serial killer when his murder victims start showing up in his jurisdiction.

684884.title: Don't Breathe
684884.description: A group of teens breaks into a blind man's home, thinking they'll get away with the perfect crime but get more than they bargained for once inside.

690311.title: The Reader
690311.description: In post-WWII Germany, a law student finds the older woman with whom he had an affair eight years ago, among Nazi prison guards being tried for murder.

694011.title: Vice
694011.description: This acclaimed biopic explores how Dick Cheney quietly wielded immense power as George W. Bush's Vice President, reshaping the U.S. and the globe.

694577.title: American Reunion
694577.description: The whole American Pie gang returns to East Great Falls, Michigan to make their reunion into the most outrageous weekend since high school.

0300005628.title: The Hour
0300005628.description: A journalist, a producer, an anchorman, and their crew take great risks to investigate stories for their nightly news program in Cold War-era England.

0300004985.title: Midsomer Murders
0300004985.description: A married veteran Detective Chief Inspector and his young sergeant investigate murders in the quaint, quirky villages of England’s Midsomer County.

0300005673.title: Houdini
0300005673.description: This fascinating miniseries explores the life and work of acclaimed magician Harry Houdini: from his rise to fame, to his surprising spy affiliation.

0300007492.title: Toradora! (Dubbed)
0300007492.description: A teen who is feared because he has his father’s same intense eyes becomes uneasy pals with his crush, a short-tempered hothead who likes his friend.

0300007679.title: The Chosen
0300007679.description: Witness the life of Christ through the ordinary people who connected with him through miracles and everyday interactions that changed the world.

0300008096.title: The Dick Van Dyke Show
0300008096.description: Laugh along to one of television's most beloved shows, centering on a TV comedy writer, his charming wife, and goofy office colleagues.

03325.title: Highlander
03325.description: As one of the immortals, entities who have waged a war between good and evil for centuries, a 400-year-old Scotsman fights for his destiny.

0300009369.title: Miranda
0300009369.description: An offbeat comedy series about Miranda Hart, a socially inept joke shop owner who digs her way out of—and into—awkward situations.

0300008835.title: Sanctuary
0300008835.description: As gene therapy, transplants and cloning offer hope for humanity, a dark side of evolution produces monsters a select few are brave enough to take on.

02348.title: Duck Dynasty
02348.description: Follow the Robertsons as they run a multi-million dollar sporting empire and face everything from beavers to business deals, in this reality series.

02166.title: Merlin
02166.description: The young wizard Merlin must keep his talent hidden in a kingdom where magic is banned as he and the future King Arthur face their destinies.

0300006058.title: The Client List
0300006058.description: Jennifer Love Hewitt stars as Riley, a newly single mother who accepts employment at a day spa which offers some scandalous services.

0300005636.title: The Fall
0300005636.description: The acclaimed crime series about a grim and gripping battle of wits between a brazen serial killer and a top-notch detective out to stop him.

02158.title: Q.I.
02158.description: QIis the Rose d'Or comedy quiz show full of quirky facts in which contestants are rewarded more if their answers are 'quite interesting'.

0300009246.title: Line of Duty
0300009246.description: Under the supervision of Superintendent Ted Hastings, British detectives in anti-corruption police unit AC-12 investigate suspected dirty cops.

0300009219.title: Quantico
0300009219.description: FBI recruits form friendships while training at Quantico Base. But relationships are tested when one of them becomes a suspect in a terrorist attack.

0300007799.title: Blue Mountain State
0300007799.description: Three new athletes on a top college football team learn the extreme high and low of being among the chosen few who are worshiped and tested on campus.

0300006342.title: Shameless
0300006342.description: In the Gallagher home, chaos is king, as the unconventional family runs through endless scams, affairs, and petty crimes throughout Manchester.

0300005170.title: Hustle
0300005170.description: An ex-street thief and a master of complex, long hustles lead a sophisticated group of con artists in stealing from greedy power players in London.

0300005653.title: Ascension
0300005653.description: Back in 1963, the U.S. government sent hundreds of citizens on a century-long voyage to a new world. Fifty years later, chaos breaks out on the ship.

0300005043.title: This Is England '86
0300005043.description: Mod revival takes the nation by storm in mid-'80s UK as a young man and his friends transition into adulthood, grappling with changes along the way.

03697.title: V
03697.description: When human-looking aliens known as Visitors appear in every major city U.S. promoting peace, an FBI counter-terrorist discovers their deadly plot.

0300007917.title: Secrets and Lies
0300007917.description: Juliette Lewis stars as a determined and brilliant detective whose latest murder case challenges her and her team with a family’s secrets and lies.

03400.title: Afro Samurai
03400.description: He's a legend with an ice cold soul and a jones for revenge: Afro Samurai. As a kid, he saw his father slaughtered. Now a man, Afro journeys to the mountain to face destiny. The perpetrators are gonna get what they deserve. Starring Samuel L. Jackson.

02064.title: Wibbly Pig
02064.description: Wibbly Pig is an animated preschool comedy series that takes the daily routine of a young child and finds humour and fun in every part of it. Wibbly simply does what children do. From day to day activities like getting into bed,wrapping a present or climbing a tree, to fantasy play like meeting a giant or going to the moon. Wibbly moves seamlessly in and out of fantasy play echoing the way children really interact and play. Wibbly turns the simplest tasks into a comedy routine, sharing it with his very best friend – the viewer.

0300006337.title: Peep Show
0300006337.description: This acclaimed, brilliant comedy tracks the everyday occurances of a pair of highly dysfunctional, well-meaning London roommates.

0300006335.title: Detectorists
0300006335.description: Follow two oddball metal detectorists as they painstakingly plough through the literal and figurative tracks and fields of life in search of treasure.

04717.title: Cosmos: A Spacetime Odyssey
04717.description: Join acclaimed astrophysicist Neil deGrasse Tyson on a journey through space and time in an effort to discover humanity’s place within the universe.

0300007796.title: Project Runway
0300007796.description: Models and fashion icons judge the works of clothing designers in this intense reality competition series that showcases up-and-coming artists.

0300007821.title: Toradora!
0300007821.description: A boy cursed with his father’s icy eyes teams up with his crush’s best friend, a violent girl named Taiga, as they try to woo their love interests.

03320.title: Hell's Kitchen
03320.description: Renowned restauranteur Gordon Ramsay hosts a fierce competition for aspiring chefs, as they vie for a prestigious job at one of his eateries.

02176.title: Mr. Bean: The Animated Series
02176.description: Bean is back! Join him, alongside his best friend Teddy and his long-suffering landlady, for more zany mishaps that surround his daily life.

0300009281.title: Everybody Hates Chris
0300009281.description: Comedian Chris Rock narrates the hilarious, touching story of a teenager growing up as the eldest of three children in Brooklyn during the 1980s.

0300005101.title: Doc Martin
0300005101.description: A socially awkward doctor leaves London for a scenic village in Cornwall where he cares for the locals, becomes a part of their lives, and finds love.

0300006767.title: Heartland
0300006767.description: Alberta sisters and their grandfather spend their years on the family ranch, where they must work through complicated issues together.

04631.title: Degrassi: The Next Generation
04631.description: Long-running TV-series, acclaimed for its powerful realism in taking on the life-changing issues facing a group of friends at a Toronto high school.

01114.title: The Lost Room
01114.description: After his daughter disappears from a mysterious hotel room that vanishes from reality, a detective seeks a series of mystical keys to bring her back.

0300009137.title: So You Think You Can Dance
0300009137.description: Skilled dancers showcase their talents in various dance styles while competing to be crowned America's favorite dancer.

0300007764.title: Pokémon the Series: Black & White
0300007764.description: Ash and Pikachu are off to the distant Unova region, where they'll encounter new friends, new rivals, new challenges, and all-new Pokémon! Upon arrival, Ash meets aspiring Dragon Master Iris, full of spirit and determination, and Pokémon Connoisseur Cilan, who is always available to lend his expertise. Above all, Ash will need plenty of new Pokémon on his team if he wants to win Unova's tournaments and Gym badges. Following his every move is the criminal trio of Team Rocket, with sinister new schemes and a fresh resolve to catch Pikachu! Then there's the mysterious N...is he a friend or a foe, and what is his connection with the secret organization known as Team Plasma? And what is Team Plasma planning to do with one of the Legendary Pokémon of the Unova region? Once this adventure starts, the excitement won't stop!

0300005236.title: Outnumbered
0300005236.description: The comedic trials of South London parents struggling to get through the day raising three rambunctious children.

0300008044.title: The Inbetweeners
0300008044.description: Four friends in public school enjoy their last years of shenanigans, as they prepare to face the real world in this hilarious series.

0300007907.title: Brickleberry
0300007907.description: Daniel Tosh stars as the lead voice in this Comedy Central cartoon series about a group of national park rangers who are terrible at their jobs.
